{"tid":816503,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來平壤新地鐵有新型號列車 佢個資訊板仲詳細過MTR西鐵果塊！","createTime":"2018-09-12T19:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T01:05:22.000Z","uid":11598,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7dad6c01f71f49ee581bca7de625fa2b35e02602","tid":816503,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.2427junction.com/70a-1c308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.2427junction.com%2F70a-1c308.jpg&h=51c19943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起平壤地下鐵，大家係咪都係覺得好舊好蘇共feel? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以嚟無論主流媒體去平壤做節目又好 做新聞又好 <br />\n都係比呢隻 上世紀型號嘅舊車我哋睇<br />\n<br />\n但係原來平壤地下鐵已經係 2016 年有新型號列車 唔知係咪中國製造 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedTkS_YB_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSedTkS_YB_s&d=RgSJ%2F8uwmlGOYU11IwcF3TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9c5e86f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedTkS_YB_s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JmZUZpQR3vs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJmZUZpQR3vs&d=RgSJ%2F8uwmlGOYU11IwcF3TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f5d63865\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JmZUZpQR3vs</a><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<code>\n1駅間の車内の様子。平壌地下鉄の車両で初めて運行情報装置が設置された。各ドアの上（鴨居部）にLCDが2台ずつ設置され、列車の位置・次の駅・現在日時・速度・温度・湿度・乗換案内・天気等が表示される。2015年に製造され、2016年1月1日より営業運転を開始した。\n</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>\n1個站距離嘅車內環境，平壤地鐵列車首次加入行車情報裝置，每度門上面都有兩個LCD Moon，顯示列車而家係邊，下個站（而家MTR有嘅），而家嘅日期，列車速度，溫度濕度，轉車資訊，天氣等等。2015年製造，2016年1月1日開始投入服務\n</code><br />\n<br />\n冷氣車廂，車廂兩邊都設有關愛座 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e02e03a9d60f39bebd0264644a512e77a00db8e","tid":816503,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"其實我好好奇，北韓按照金仔呢個進度，社會主義最盡可以發展到點"},{"pid":"98c14ea5a2fc94ae26b97577656b607770b79b4d","tid":816503,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e02e03a9d60f39bebd0264644a512e77a00db8e","tid":816503,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"其實我好好奇，北韓按照金仔呢個進度，社會主義最盡可以發展到點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實北韓已經唔係完全社會主義，向緊中國同古巴果種模式轉變緊"},{"pid":"e82fb43dd5a5f9ab7fb965cae06f3d26e548459a","tid":816503,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c14ea5a2fc94ae26b97577656b607770b79b4d","tid":816503,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e02e03a9d60f39bebd0264644a512e77a00db8e","tid":816503,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:34:23.000Z","msg":"其實我好好奇，北韓按照金仔呢個進度，社會主義最盡可以發展到點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實北韓已經唔係完全社會主義，向緊中國同古巴果種模式轉變緊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T19:45:57.000Z","msg":"北泡應該會響金仔管治下進行首次改革開放 由計劃經濟變混合經濟體<br />\n其實北泡而家無論響經濟人民自由已經比以前有唔少改變<br />\n男女可以一齊出街 有手提電話3g neteork <br />\n平壤大商場food court有西式野食等等"},{"pid":"604b140ba626714cfdee97c12295ba317bf35f98","tid":816503,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e82fb43dd5a5f9ab7fb965cae06f3d26e548459a","tid":816503,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c14ea5a2fc94ae26b97577656b607770b79b4d","tid":816503,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e02e03a9d60f39bebd0264644a512e77a00db8e","tid":816503,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c